# Brewfile for Kamaete - macOS Developer Setup
# This file defines all the essential CLI tools and GUI applications
# to be installed via Homebrew for a complete development environment.
#
# Usage:
#   brew bundle          # Install everything in this file
#   brew bundle cleanup  # Remove packages not listed in this file

